  "texts": [
    "To better analyze the quality of the summaries generated by the models, we randomly select 10 instances from the BookSum dataset and conduct a human evaluation.",
    "The evaluators we have recruited are graduate and doctoral candidates with specializations in Computer Science or Computational Linguistics, each possessing advanced proficiency in English.",
    "They receive compensation at the University's established hourly rate.",
    "Evaluators are asked to read the corresponding original document, as well as five candidate summaries (from FFT, LoRA, and RST p w -LoRA with Vicuna backbone, GPT-4 and human).",
    "The human evaluators are blind to the condition, i.e."
  ]
}